  <p class="text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-4">Admins and maintainers also have access to these endpoints and see all tenants via <code class="bg-white/5 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[#38bdf8] text-sm font-mono">/mine</code>.</p>

